    {
      "id": "a4d0e510a287b717684e913e1ea180d86721ecd0",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 125,
        "name": "James Simmons",
        "email": "jsimmons@infradead.org",
        "username": "jsimmons"
      },
      "date": "2022-04-28 12:45:24.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nAlso I noticed:\n\nchecking for the distutils Python package... yes\nchecking for Python include path... <string>:1: DeprecationWarning: The distutils package is deprecated and slated for removal in Python 3.12. Use setuptools or check PEP 632 for p\notential alternatives\n<string>:1: DeprecationWarning: The distutils.sysconfig module is deprecated, use sysconfig instead\n\nDoes RHEL9 clients show the same thing?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "240d9c868a5a43b9174509989204cf4974856f03",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 131,
        "name": "Jian Yu",
        "email": "yujian@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "yujian"
      },
      "date": "2022-04-29 17:51:50.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Also I noticed:\n > \n > checking for the distutils Python package... yes\n > checking for Python include path... <string>:1: DeprecationWarning:\n > The distutils package is deprecated and slated for removal in\n > Python 3.12. Use setuptools or check PEP 632 for p\n > otential alternatives\n > <string>:1: DeprecationWarning: The distutils.sysconfig module is\n > deprecated, use sysconfig instead\n > \n > Does RHEL9 clients show the same thing?\n\nNo. On RHEL 9.0 Beta with kernel 5.15.13:\n checking whether to build Lustre tests... checking for python3... /usr/bin/python3\n checking for a version of Python >= '3.6.0'... yes\n checking for the distutils Python package... yes\n checking for Python include path... -I/usr/include/python3.9\n checking for Python library path... -L/usr/lib64 -lpython3.9\n checking for Python site-packages path... /usr/lib/python3.9/site-packages",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "91e3d5bc1d72a33ccfb65144a319b60a4742513a",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 131,
        "name": "Jian Yu",
        "email": "yujian@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "yujian"
      },
      "date": "2022-04-29 19:23:18.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nPython version on RHEL 9.0 Beta is 3.9.6, while on Ubuntu 22.04 it is 3.10.4.\n\nAccording to https://peps.python.org/pep-0632/:\n In Python 3.10 and 3.11, distutils will be formally marked as deprecated. And in Python 3.12, distutils will no longer be installed.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
